data.text:
Description:

Autograph and photo of Vicente Aleixandre. Vicente Aleixandre (1898 - 1984) was a Spanish poet who was born in Seville. Aleixandre received the Nobel Prize for Literature in 1977 for a creative poetic writing. Autograph written in pen over photo. Dimensions: 3.5x 5.5" card in VG condition. Reverse has seller notes with 7/6/68 date. All items carefully packed to avoid damage from moisture and rough handling. Seller Inventory # 039668
